<span lang=3D"EN-US">Graduated in Commerce in 1991 and associated with the =
Madras Dyslexia Association ( MDA) for over 15 years.</span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"font-family:Calibri,Arial,Helvetica,sans-se=
